1
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:52,759
Dr. Jiang

2
00:00:55,439 --> 00:00:57,520
Thank you

3
00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:00,359
for all this time

4
00:01:01,719 --> 00:01:05,280
you spent with us two old folks

5
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:08,519
playing house.

6
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:11,400
Regrets over missed chances

7
00:01:11,959 --> 00:01:13,480
can never be made up for.

8
00:01:16,159 --> 00:01:17,319
If back then,

9
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:19,519
I'd had the chance to say goodbye to Grandma...

10
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:27,840
The one I worry about most

11
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:32,400
is you.

12
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:35,640
Don't hold a grudge

13
00:01:36,439 --> 00:01:37,920
against your father.

14
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:42,840
Get along with him.

15
00:01:43,799 --> 00:01:45,239
Hurry up and...

16
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:46,640
and...

17
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:49,359
start a family.

18
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,439
Only then can Grandma

19
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,319
finally

20
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:58,280
rest at ease.

21
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,719
Dr. Jiang,

22
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:04,879
you are

23
00:02:06,079 --> 00:02:07,120
a good person.

24
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,159
If

25
00:02:15,319 --> 00:02:18,199
my son one day

26
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,520
comes back,

27
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:25,759
please tell him for me

28
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,120
that in

29
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,439
the kitchen,

30
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:36,919
in the southeast corner cupboard,

31
00:02:38,039 --> 00:02:39,719
I left him

32
00:02:40,639 --> 00:02:45,319
his favorite pickled vegetables.

33
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,800
Tell him to remember

34
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,120
to come home

35
00:02:57,479 --> 00:03:00,400
and see his father.

36
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,599
No.

37
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,280
No.

38
00:03:15,639 --> 00:03:16,319
Grandma.

39
00:03:16,879 --> 00:03:17,560
Grandma.

40
00:03:18,199 --> 00:03:19,560
Grandma!

41
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:52,520
My dear.

42
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,400
Let's go home.

43
00:03:57,039 --> 00:03:58,719
Come home with me.

44
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,439
Elder Chun, Younger Chun

45
00:04:03,879 --> 00:04:05,719
are still waiting for us.

46
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,480
We've made up our minds.

47
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,759
This way, we can help more people.

48
00:05:43,639 --> 00:05:45,279
If I hadn't been suspended,

49
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:47,199
I could've saved her.

50
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:55,800
By the time Auntie Jiang was brought in,

51
00:05:57,319 --> 00:05:58,600
it was already too late.

52
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,519
It shouldn't have ended like this.

53
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:21,600
I reminded her again and again

54
00:06:22,319 --> 00:06:24,720
to watch Uncle Ge's oral condition.

55
00:06:26,279 --> 00:06:28,920
But I never thought to examine her.

56
00:06:31,959 --> 00:06:32,759
It's me.

57
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,560
It's my fault.

58
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:38,519
If I'd just been a little more careful,

59
00:06:40,199 --> 00:06:41,120
maybe none of this

60
00:06:41,199 --> 00:06:43,560
would've turned out this way.

61
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:46,800
Tiancai.

62
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,600
Jiang Tiancai.

63
00:06:49,079 --> 00:06:50,439
Jiang Tiancai, look at me.

64
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,000
Look at me.

65
00:06:54,439 --> 00:06:56,480
No one wanted this to happen.

66
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,920
Auntie Jiang had diabetes

67
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:01,800
with submandibular space infection.

68
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:03,600
Complications like that

69
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,319
are inherently hard to prevent.

70
00:07:05,839 --> 00:07:07,399
And it progressed so rapidly.

71
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,279
We did everything within our power

72
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,639
to give her the best care.

73
00:08:22,079 --> 00:08:22,920
How is he?

74
00:08:26,759 --> 00:08:27,839
Listless.

75
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:30,759
I've never seen him like this before.

76
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:32,919
Then do you...

77
00:08:33,399 --> 00:08:34,840
really believe what the news is saying?

78
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,519
Of course not.

79
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,200
I found the original video you wanted.

80
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:44,159
We all know that patient's family.

81
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,039
It's Mengmeng's Dad.

82
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:01,159
After a tooth is fractured or knocked out by trauma,

83
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:02,879
avoid touching the tooth root directly,

84
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,720
or wrapping it in tissue or similar items.

85
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:07,519
Place it in saline solution or milk,

86
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,759
or under the tongue.

87
00:09:08,919 --> 00:09:10,039
Within the Golden Thirty Minutes,

88
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,039
replantation can be achieved.

